<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600;700;800&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Poppins', 'sans-serif'],
                        heading: ['Montserrat', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#4F46E5',
                        secondary: '#EC4899',
                        dark: '#1e1b4b',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>

    <style>
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards; }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        .animate-float { animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center">

    <div class="text-center px-4 animate-fade-in">
        
        <!-- Illustration -->
        <div class="mb-8 animate-float">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-train text-7xl text-white opacity-50"></i>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Error Code -->
        <h1 class="font-heading text-8xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">404</h1>
        
        <!-- Error Message -->
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Oops! Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
            Sepertinya Anda mencoba naik kereta ke stasiun yang tidak ada. Mari kita kembali ke jalur yang benar.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/" class="bg-white text-primary font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-home mr-2"></i>Kembali ke Beranda
            </a>
            <a href="/cek-pesanan" class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-white/30 transition">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-ticket mr-2"></i>Cek Pesanan
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
